Stores project dependencies.

Example:

fastapi==0.112.0
uvicorn==0.30.0
pandas==2.2.2
Why Use requirements.txt?

If your friend downloads your project:

git clone project

They can install everything with one command.

Example 1

Create file:

requirements.txt

Content:

fastapi
uvicorn
Example 2

Install requirements.

pip install -r requirements.txt
Example 3

Generate requirements.

pip freeze > requirements.txt
Example 4

View requirements file.

fastapi==0.112.0
uvicorn==0.30.0